Job Description
THE ROAD OF SUCCESS.
Abu Dhabi Motors, is the top-ranked and best selling importer for BMW. Alpina, MINI, Rolls-Royce and AC Schnitzer in the Middle East, the Rolls-Royce 2012 and 2013 Global Dealer of the Year as well as Global Winner of Excellence in Sales Award for "Leadership in Luxury Class" in the BMW Group. Our ever-expanding network located in Abu Dhabi and Al Ain are looking for top-quality individuals to join our dynamic world-class organization in Abu Dhabi. Successful candidates will enjoy exceptional tax-free remuneration opportunities.
We are defined by excellence and hold everything we do to the highest standards. Our employee satisfaction is impeccable and our expansion sustains the companies quest towards superior customer services. We are looking for enthusiastic individuals who are eager to be part of a strong community of the best professionals in the industry. Some of the following positions require several employees:
Painters and Denters
- Experience in this field is preferred.
- Must be in good health since the work requires physical endurance and good eyesight.
- Training will be provided for those showing exemplary potential.Apply Instructions for This Job
